            <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-primary">11.1 Limited Warranties</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-muted">We warrant that:</p>
            <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-muted">
              <li>Our Services will perform substantially in accordance with their documentation</li>
              <li>Hardware products will be free from material defects for 12 months from delivery</li>
              <li>We will provide Services with reasonable skill and care</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-primary">11.2 Disclaimers</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
              Except as expressly stated, our Services are provided "as is" and "as available." We disclaim all other
              warranties, express or implied, including warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose,
              and non-infringement.
            </p>

            <div class="my-8 border-t border-subtle"></div>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary">12. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-muted">To the maximum extent permitted by law:</p>
            <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-muted">
